OL,7,FA taxi driver who ran over and killed
OL,8,Fa 32-year-old man 15 minutes after
OL,9,Fbeing stopped by the police or
OL,10,Fspeeding has been jailed.
OL,12,FDaniel Beames, known to his friends as
OL,13,FBeamer, had been on a night out in
OL,14,FCheltenham on 17 December 2021 when he
OL,15,Fwas hit by a taxi as he crossed
OL,16,FLansdown Road at around 10.50pm.
