OL,7,FShakoor Ahmed, aged 46 and of Conduit
OL,8,FStreet, Gloucester, pleaded guilty
OL,9,Fearlier this month to causing the
OL,10,Fdeath of Daniel Beames by dangerous
OL,11,Fdriving.
OL,13,FHe appeared at Gloucester Crown Court
OL,14,Fon Thursday 2 May where he was
OL,15,Fsentenced to six years and 10 months
OL,16,Fin prison by Judge Rupert Lowe.
OL,18,FThe court heard Ahmed had been stopped
OL,19,Fby police 15 minutes before the
OL,20,Fcollision when he had been warned
OL,21,Fabout his speed.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/13
