OL,7,FHowever, Ahmed failed to heed the
OL,8,Fwarning and continued to drive at
OL,9,Fexcessive speeds.
OL,11,FPicking up a fare in Gloucester, who
OL,12,Fwere travelling to Cheltenham, he
OL,13,Fboasted to them that he had already
OL,14,Fbeen stopped by police that evening
OL,15,Ffor driving too fast.
