OL,7,FEmily Evans, prosecuting, told the
OL,8,Fcourt: "(The passenger) described how,
OL,9,Fat one point, there was nothing in
OL,10,Ffront of them and he felt the
OL,11,Facceleration of the vehicle push him
OL,12,Fback into his seat.
OL,14,F"As soon as they got onto the Golden
OL,15,FValley bypass, Ahmed told his
OL,16,Fpassengers that he could do 100mph
OL,17,Falong that stretch.
OL,19,F"He did indeed get up to 100mph,
OL,20,Ftravelling along the Golden Valley in
OL,21,Frecord time."
