OL,7,FOnce in Cheltenham, Ahmed continued to
OL,8,Fdrive at speed before getting caught
OL,9,Fbehind a slower moving vehicle on
OL,10,FLansdowne Road.
OL,12,FOvertaking the car, Ahmed pulled back
OL,13,Fin front of it as Mr Beames was
OL,14,Fcrossing the road, colliding with him.
OL,16,FAhmed was said to have his foot fully
OL,17,Fon the accelerator moments before the
OL,18,Fcollision, pushing the car to 53mph on
OL,19,Fa 40mph road.
