OL,7,FMs Evans said: "Had he been travelling
OL,8,Fat 40mph the risk of fatality would
OL,9,Fhave been 30%. At 53mph, that
OL,10,Fincreases to an 80% chance."
OL,12,FMr Beames was taken to Southmead
OL,13,FHospital in Bristol but died from his
OL,14,Finjuries the following day.
OL,16,FDaniel's mother, Yvette White, told
OL,17,Fthe court: "Daniel was my only son, my
OL,18,Ffriend, my protector and my pride.
