OL,7,F"He was kind, generous, funny,
OL,8,Fempathic, sporty, adventurous,
OL,9,Fintelligent, rational, a great artist,
OL,10,Fa fantastic landscape gardener, a
OL,11,Fbrilliant chef, extremely loveable and
OL,12,Fa perfect son.
OL,14,F"Daniel's life has gone, and mine and
OL,15,Fthe rest of my family's lives are
OL,16,Fruined. The driver not only took away
OL,17,Fmy son's life but he has destroyed
OL,18,Fmine as well."
