OL,7,FDaniel's partner, Jess Beames, told
OL,8,Fthe court the family had been handed a
OL,9,Flife sentence.
OL,11,FPaying tribute to him, she said that
OL,12,Fher son, Barney, who had been just six
OL,13,Fat the time of the collision, was
OL,14,Fstill coming to terms with Daniel's
OL,15,Fdeath.
OL,17,FSpeaking to the court, Jess said:
OL,18,F"There is a melancholy that lives on
OL,19,Fwithin my bones. I've been stripped
OL,20,Fentirely of who I am and I will never
OL,21,Fget used to Dan being dead.
