OL,7,FHe said: "The officers involved were
OL,8,Fnot in possession of a crystal ball
OL,9,Fand there is no criticism of their
OL,10,Fhumane and appropriate actions at that
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,F"In light of what followed, you did
OL,14,Fnot take the issue of your speeding
OL,15,Fseriously.
OL,17,F"I characterise the dangerous driving
OL,18,Fcame from a gross arrogance on your
OL,19,Fpart, meaning you felt you could speed
OL,20,Fwhen you wanted to.
