OL,11,Ftheir driving but it was no deterrent
OL,12,Fto Ahmed.
OL,14,F"His selfish actions have lead to the
OL,15,Ftragic death of this young man,
OL,16,Fputting Daniel's family through
OL,17,Fneedless heartache and suffering."
